Class GameObjectManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • gremlins.GameObjectManager

  • public class GameObjectManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages game objects, including walls, wizard, gremlins, projectiles, and game levels.

        public int collisionWithWall(double nextX,
                             double nextY,
                             GameObject object)
        Checks for collision of the wizard with walls at specified coordinates.
        Parameters:
        nextX - The next x-coordinate to check
        nextY - The next y-coordinate to check
        object - The game object (wizard) to check collisions for
        Returns:
        0 if no collision, 1 if collision with stone wall, 2 if collision with brick wall
